<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SUNPARNAK MEI ALH</title>
<key>A</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thlarau tthanghnak mei, a hung kang lio cang
 Hmun khat hnu hmun khat, a kang thluahmah cang
 Alh thluahmah in aa kangh cang
 Sunparnak Mei alh.
 Thlarau thimi hna, an hung tho than cang
 Temhtonmi hna zong, an hung luat than cang
 Alh thluahmah in aa kangh cang
 Sunparnak Mei alh.

[C1]
   Thlarau, Mei alh kang cang seh, Taksa sinak ziam dih seh
   Remnak ram lei ah kan hruai than, Sunparnak Mei alh,
   Thlarau, Mei alh kang cang seh, Taksa sinak ziam dih seh
   Remnak ram lei ah kan hruai than, Sunparnak Mei alh.</lyrics>
</song>